products.title: William Morris Compton Buttercup Roller Blind
products.description: A stunning conversational piece, the compton buttercup roller blind comes with a story to tell. Part of their william morris range, in collaboration with the v&a, compton was produced in 1896 for compton hall, near wolverhampton, the house of laurence w. Hodson.
